name: Stacey Threadgill
text: What a great family experience! The grounds are very well maintained and clean. The shop has any and bait needed, and stocked with snacks and beverages. The fishing is top notch, and you could not ask for any better hospitality than what Doug and Allie has shown. We were blown away with the abundance of catfish, brim, crappie, and BIG BASS!! we are already planning our next road trip here!!❤

text: Was fun no fish for us but still going to try
